text: The Frontier Middle School shooting was a school shooting that occurred on February 2, 1996, at Frontier Middle School in Moses Lake, Washington, United States. The shooting was perpetrated by 14-year-old student Barry Loukaitis. Category:School shootings in the United States Category:1996 in the United States Category:1996 events Category:1996 crimes
title: 1996 Frontier Middle School shooting
